snippet.title: Undertale Yellow: But Blue WILD EAST UPDATE [UTY MOD]
snippet.description:
Hi hi HELLO!!! 
The Wild East update for Undertale Yellow But Blue is now OUT!

Download it HERE: https://gamejolt.com/games/UTYBB/900920
or HERE: https://gamebanana.com/mods/502229
Big ol' thanks to Sockhead (https://s0ckh3adstudios.tumblr.com/) for creating Flo and the thumbnail of this video.
Note: This version of the mod goes only up to the start of Steamworks, you will know when the mod ends.
